# ArminC-Keyboard-Layout

Custom gaming keyboard preset with binds for [Keyboard Layout Editor](http://www.keyboard-layout-editor.com/).

## Context
|  Editor menu   | Extension |
|:-------------- | --------- |
| Raw data       | .json     |
| Custom styles  | .css      |
